reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 28, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Pleasant Sweet Taste
reviews.reviewText: I previously ordered other vitamins and the taste was terrible & ended up throwing them away. Some time ago I had purchased a sugar like coated gummy vitamin at WalMart but didn't find them when I wanted to purchase them again. I found these here on Amazon & they were exactly what I had been looking for. They're like eating candy without the awful vitamin taste. I just received my 2nd bottle and will be ordering these again when I need them.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 13, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Taste so Good!! Not like vitamins!!
reviews.reviewText: I didn't realize these where sugar covered gummys n not just regular type but I was happy to c they were!!What's crazy is they taste so so good!! Like candy!! I've never found a gummy vitamin or any vitamin that didn't have at least a slight "vitamin" werid taste or after taste but this one doesn't!! They are almost to good, u would never guess they were vitamins! So definitely keep them away from children n up high!! Happy with them n will order again! Also fast shipping
